The code is released under the GNU General Public License.

This is the 3D model of my robot made in Autodesk Inventor 2012. See the folder "Rendered images" for images of the model.

The 3D model can also be viewed at the following site: http://grabcad.com/library/balancing-robot.

The Arduino board were made by the user "wam" at the Arduino forum: http://www.arduino.cc/cgi-bin/yabb2/YaBB.pl?num=1288144315/all.

The mbed board were made by Hugo Stoutjesdijk.

And the XBee module were made by Russell Donovan and downloaded from: http://grabcad.com/library/xbee-module.

For more information see my blog post at http://blog.tkjelectronics.dk/2012/02/the-balancing-robot/ or send me an email at kristianl at tkjelectronics dot dk.